message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC. The paper deals with a question answering dataset and the study of answer selection models, which are topics related to natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG) techniques, which make cs.IR and cs.LG likely sub-categories as well. Additionally, the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and artificial intelligence (AI) methods suggest cs.AI as a possible sub-category. Finally, the study of computational models and their performance on the dataset may also relate to cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
